Thumbs.db

# ---------- Private — agent instructions and LLM prompts ----------
# These files contain the agent context, prompt engineering, and
# step-by-step plan that drive Cairn's behavior. Kept out of git so
# they don't leak via the public history. They still exist locally —
# Claude Code reads them on disk at session start, and the runtime
# loads /prompts/*.md when the app boots. See note in README on
# deploying with gitignored prompts.
AGENTS.md
CLAUDE.md
KICKOFF-PROMPT.md
/prompts/
/docs/plan.md
